SAFFOLD
v.
BLACK ECONOMIC UNION OF OHIO 2019-0372 Supreme Court of Ohio. April 18, 2019

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULING

On motion of Nathalie A. Dibo and Matthew P. Yourkvitch to withdraw as counsel for appellee. Motion granted. Appellee may file a memorandum in response to jurisdiction within 30 days.
